title: Hot Jellied Eels
content:
Hot Jellied Eels are a category of item that is an intermediate ingredient to Jellied Eels. It can be cooked in The Delectable Dab Kitchen in Hopeport using the Chef profession. Recipes for the Chef profession can be found in the Chef Recipe Book.


 * Lesser Hot Jellied Eels
 * Gray Hot Jellied Eels
 * Rocky Hot Jellied Eels
 * Rord Hot Jellied Eels
 * Moray Hot Jellied Eels
 * Conger Hot Jellied Eels
 * Leopard Hot Jellied Eels
 * Greater Hot Jellied Eels
